Interface IndexFieldData<FD extends AtomicFieldData>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIndexFieldData, AbstractIndexOrdinalsFieldData, BinaryDVIndexFieldData, BinaryDVNumericIndexFieldData, BytesBinaryDVIndexFieldData, DisabledIndexFieldData, DoubleArrayIndexFieldData, FloatArrayIndexFieldData, FSTBytesIndexFieldData, GeoPointBinaryDVIndexFieldData, GeoPointCompressedIndexFieldData, GeoPointDoubleArrayIndexFieldData, GlobalOrdinalsIndexFieldData, IndexIndexFieldData, NumericDVIndexFieldData, PackedArrayIndexFieldData, PagedBytesIndexFieldData, ParentChildIndexFieldData, SortedNumericDVIndexFieldData, SortedSetDVOrdinalsIndexFieldData

    public interface IndexFieldData<FD extends AtomicFieldData>
extends IndexComponent
    Thread-safe utility class that allows to get per-segment values via the load(AtomicReaderContext) method.
